  "title": "MANICURIST",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide professional manicure and pedicure services</li><li>Apply gel, acrylic, nail art, and extensions</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of tools and workstations</li><li>Educate clients on nail care, aftercare, and available services</li><li>Stay updated on nail trends, techniques, and safety standards</li><li>Ensure excellent customer service and build a loyal client base</li><li>Manage appointments and assist in product recommendations</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience as a manicurist or nail technician</li><li>Skilled in gel polish, nail art, extensions, and classic care</li><li>Friendly, professional, and well-groomed</li><li>Strong communication and customer service skills</li><li>A passion for beauty, style, and client satisfaction</li><li>Ability to work flexible hours, including weekends</li></ul>",
